Package: intermahp3
Title: The International Model of Alcohol Harms and Policies
Version: 3.0
Authors@R:
  person(
    "Sam",
    "Churchill",
    email = "meadowschurchill@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre")
  )
Description:
  R Implementation of CISUR's International Model of Alcohol Harms and Policies.
  Intended mainly as a backend to the InterMAHP shiny app.
  Includes base functionality of group-stratified AAF Computation along with
  application to user-input Morbididty/Mortality counts and comparison of
  expected consumption scenarios.
